= James G. Blaine

James G. Blaine is a representative from Maine and is one of the leading figures of the House of representatives with his mix between Radicalism and Moderate policies.

- @Blaine_Unity: Unify the Radicals and Moderates
- @Blaine_WASP: **I HATE CATHOLICS!!**
